lyrics:
[Verse]
Barry de natte hond, always on the go
With a wagging tail, he steals the show
Running through the fields, chasing the sun
He brings joy and laughter, to everyone

[Chorus]
Barry de natte hond, your spirit so high
You light up the world, as you pass by
Barking with delight, spreading love around
Barry, our furry friend, you truly astound
